<https://w3id.org/mqto#causedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a Failure Mode to another Failure Mode that causes it, forming a causal chain. Three sub-properties (causedByWeakly, causedByModerately, causedByStrongly) express different causal strengths."@en .
