<https://w3id.org/mqto#providesSignal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/mqto/1.0> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#providesSignal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "provides signal"@en .
