# 
# https://w3id.org/mqto#upperBound
<https://w3id.org/mqto#upperBound> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#upperBound> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/mqto#Metric> .
