<https://w3id.org/mqto#upperBound> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote> "Stored as dimensionless xsd:double; unit of measurement determined by the Metric's associated Signal."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/mqto#weight
<https://w3id.org/mqto#weight> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#weight> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> _:genid1 .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#unionOf> _:genid3 .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid2 .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <https://w3id.org/mqto#FailureMode> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <https://w3id.org/mqto#Countermeasure> .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#weight> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#int> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#weight> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A relative ranking weight. For Failure Modes: severity or priority. For Countermeasures: effectiveness or preference. Provides anchor points for external ranking logic."@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#weight> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/mqto/1.0> .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#weight> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "weight"@en .
<https://w3id.org/mqto#weight> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote> "The ontology does not prescribe the ranking algorithm itself; interpretation is application-specific."@en .
