<https://w3id.org/mqto#CountermeasureStepList> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An ordered, reusable container of CountermeasureSteps. Uses an OWL-native linked list pattern (mqto:first / mqto:rest), terminated by mqto:nil."@en .
