<https://w3id.org/mqto#CountermeasureStepList> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote> "Uses explicit OWL class and property definitions instead of rdf:List for reasoner compatibility. Standard rdf:List creates known issues with OWL reasoners due to blank node handling and recursive structure reasoning. See OWL 2 Primer Section 4.2."@en .
